sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant S as Subject
  participant API as API
  participant OP as Operator
  participant DB as MongoDB
  participant WK as Worker

  S->>API: POST /privacy/requests (unauthenticated, rate-limited)
  API->>DB: record pvr_ (pending)
  API-->>S: identical generic acknowledgement (no existence signal)
  OP->>OP: verify identity out-of-band
  OP->>API: POST /admin/privacy-requests/{id}/verify (reason)
  API->>DB: audit → mark_verified (guarded) → enqueue privacy_delete
  WK->>DB: match requests + their conversations by requester email
  WK->>DB: tombstone conversations · skeletonize requests · delete feedback
  WK->>DB: store result_counts on pvr_ · audit
